data.chText: 思乡的；想家的；患怀乡病的
data.enText: sad because you are away from home and you miss your family and friends

value.def: If you are homesick, you feel unhappy because you are away from home and are missing your family, friends, and home very much.

example.ex: There were inevitable bouts of homesickness.
example.tran: 难免会涌起一阵阵的思乡情绪。
